title: Pregnant Pauses
itunes:title: Pregnant Pauses
description:
We try something different and have TWO special guests; Mike Minnick from the defunct band Curl Up and Die and Dave Gorum the lead designer at Carbon Made. Rather than reviewing records, we simply talk media and discuss The Bachelorette, Jesu, comics and a bunch of other things.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
